CLONING

The following shell commands clone this repo and submodules.

   $ git clone git@github.com:Learnosity/mathcore.git
   $ cd mathcore
   $ git submodule init
   $ git submodule update


BUILDING

Built files are placed in ./lib/

   $ cd build
   $ make


TESTING

The library must be built before it can be tested.

   $ cd tests
   $ make all

MERGING

Merge a branch into master

   git checkout master
   git merge feature-branch
   git submodule update
   cd build
   make

You should now have an updated mathcore.js and chemcore.js in the ../lib.
Follow the "TESTING" directions to be sure.
